Name: Fruit Mess
About the game: Fruit mess is an unusual casual match-3 game. A distinctive feature is the construction of objects not only horizontally or vertically but also diagonally. You can build interesting and very long chains of fruit and get even more points. Manage to collect the necessary account before the time expires and go to the next level. Good luck.
